Raquel Lee https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Raquel_Lee 0 Raquel Yvette Lee (born October 13, 1986) is an American actress, writer, producer, director, comedian, and voice actress who appeared on "The Amanda Show" during the show's first season. After Season 1 of "The Amanda Show" ended Raquel left the show and was replaced by Josh Peck. She also provided the voice of Nubia Gross on "The Proud Family" from 2001 to 2005. She also co-starred with Tahj Mowry, Mark Curry and Dawnn Lewis in "The Poof Point". On July 14, 2016 Raquel and Edouard welcomed their daughter Celine Rose Bolleau.
